text.section: "Commissioner" means the commissioner of the Department of Insurance of this state.
"Department" means the Department of Insurance of this state, unless context otherwise requires.

law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 908, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 187, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 131, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 301, subtit. 1, sec. 5, effective June 18, 1970.
